A Better Answer for Pain Care | axialHealthcare










































































615-345-3555 




















About Us
axialHealthcare began when a group of physicians, scientists, technologists, analysts and entrepreneurs banded together and passionately committed themselves to improving the health of patients in pain.

As chronic pain has become more prevalent, with over 100 million Americans experiencing an episode of pain each year, healthcare costs have far exceeded their previous levels and opioid use has escalated into an epidemic.
axialHealthcare has pioneered an evidence-driven, predictive pain management solution that empowers insurers and equips care professionals with the ability to curb the overuse of opioids, align expenses, ensure safety, and attain optimal pain patient outcomes.

















Our Mission
To improve the well-being of patients in pain, while creating value for our partners.
A serious episode of acute or chronic pain too often leaves patients suffering with their underlying symptoms while feeling a sense of abandonment, confusion and frustration with their Insurers pain care delivery network. Similarly, well intentioned physicians and care givers are most frequently unable to readily discern opioid patient risk factors, apply personalized evidence supported care, and to safely administer opioid prescription regimens. axialHealthcare is committed to resolving these enormous problems and to continuously create value for all involved.










Our Values
At axialHealthcare, we are deeply committed to five core values.



Integrity
Fairly, honestly and transparently conducting all aspects of our activity.


Alliance Building
Allying with like-minded partners to collaborate around our patients.


Innovation
Continuously evaluating, testing, proving and deploying new pain care value drivers.


Compassion
Enveloping pain patients with caring listening and support, when they need us most.


Performance
Establishing clear expectations, being fully accountable to our partners and delivering the results.












Leadership
axialHealthcare is comprised of a band of experienced clinicians, operators, innovators and health care pioneers who are passionate about pain care.








