Axial Healthcare, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 8:18 AM ET
Health Care Technology

Company Overview of Axial Healthcare, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Axial Healthcare, Inc. provides pain medication and pain care management solutions for health insurers and care professionals. It offers axialInsight, an analytics engine that enables users to find correlation, causation, and predictive analytics; axialPractice that provide practitioners with insight into their opioid patient panel and peer benchmarking; and axialNetwork that organizes the top performing pain practitioners within a health plan. The company also provides axialPatient that collects self-reported and biometric sensor data; tracks triggers of chronic episodes; and empowers the patient in reducing their pain, and managing symptoms and side effects. Axial Healthcare, Inc. was inco...
Axial Healthcare, Inc. provides pain medication and pain care management solutions for health insurers and care professionals. It offers axialInsight, an analytics engine that enables users to find correlation, causation, and predictive analytics; axialPractice that provide practitioners with insight into their opioid patient panel and peer benchmarking; and axialNetwork that organizes the top performing pain practitioners within a health plan. The company also provides axialPatient that collects self-reported and biometric sensor data; tracks triggers of chronic episodes; and empowers the patient in reducing their pain, and managing symptoms and side effects. Axial Healthcare, Inc. was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Nashville, Tennessee.
