Axial Healthcare, Inc. Key Developments

axial Healthcare, Inc. Appoints Patrick J. Kennedy as Director
Jun 15 17
axialHealthcare, Inc. announced that former U.S. Representative Patrick J. Kennedy is joining the Board of Directors to help inform and expand the company’s substance use disorder capabilities. Patrick Kennedy’s personal story and professional career make him a perfect addition to axialHealthcare’s Board of Directors. Kennedy has lived experience with addiction to opioid medication following back surgery and has a long history of advocating for access to mental health care, specifically in the area of addiction treatment. He devoted much of his 16-year career in Congress to ending the stigma associated with mental illness through his work, including authoring the Mental Health Parity and Addiction Equity Act of 2008.


