Company Description


Axial Healthcare, Inc. provides pain management solution solutions. Its solutions include axialInsight, axialPractice, axialNetwork and axialPatient. The axialInsight is an analytics engine that enables users to find correlation, causation and predictive analytics. The axialPractice provides practitioners with insight into their opioid patient panel and peer benchmarking. The axialNetwork organizes the top performing pain practitioners within a health plan. The axialPatient gives patients a voice in their pain care through a pain management app. The company was founded by Kevin Kirkpatrick and Paul McCurry in 2012 and is headquartered in Nashville, TN.




